title: One year of Google Search Central
description:
A year ago, we launched our new site and announced that we were leaving our beloved
      name, Google Webmasters, behind for a new moniker: Google Search Central. This year, we've been
      working with our internal SEO team to improve our content, writing lots of new documentation,
      migrating 13 local language blogs, and developing a new checklist for our home page.
